<h2 id="using-related-content">Using related content</h2>

<p>The realted content component is a vertical list of links, signposting users to other content that might be useful.</p>

<p>Related content links shouldnâ€™t be the same as the links used in the page <a href="contents">contents</a> or in the <a href="breadcrumbs">breadcrumbs</a>. They should signpost users to relevant content held in different sections of the website or on external websites.</p>

<p>Related content should be positioned on the right side of a page or at the bottom, below the main body of content.</p>
